  "Description": "MODIFICATIONS:\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                DATASTAGE               CODE                           DATE\nDEVELOPER             DATE                TICKET/PROJECT         DESCRIPTION                                                                                      ENVIRONMENT          REVIEWER                 REVIEW\n-----------------------------    ----------------------     ------------------------------        -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------  ------------------------------    ------------------------------       --------------------\nSrikanth Mettpalli      08/02/2013        5114                              Original Programming                                                                            EnterpriseWrhsDevl       \nKishore Goud           10/02/2018         5802                             Added weekly void table                                                                       EnterpriseDevl            Kalyan Neelam             2020-09-15\n\nAnnotations:\nJob Name: IdsEdwWMbrVoidDrvrLoad\nRead Load File created in the IdsEdwWMbrVoidDrvrExtract Job\nCopy Stage for buffer\nDelete then Insert the W_MBR_VOID_DRVR Data.\nLoad rejects are redirected into a Reject file"
